question:
What do we need to make an <b>image</b> or <b>VIDEO</b> (also called <b>replaced elements</b>) to apply <code>object fit</code> property?
<pre>img{
      ...
      ...
      object-fit: contain; /* or object-fit: cover; */
}</pre>

answer:
img{
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      object-fit: contain; /* or object-fit: cover; */
}

